1.) YOUR NAME? Danae Johnson
2.) YOUR AGE? 16 (17 in 9 days!!!)
3.) WHERE DO YOU LIVE? I live in Idaho.
4.) POST A PICTURE (OR A FEW!) OF YOURSELF HERE!
 I'm on the Right.

5.) HOW DID YOU HEAR ABOUT THE JONAS BROTHERS? I heard of them when they appeared on TRL for the first time.
6.) WHAT WAS YOUR FIRST IMPRESSION? I thought that they were just another Boy Band. Then I actually listened to their music, and now I love them.
7.) HAVE YOU EVER SEEN THEM LIVE? IF SO, WHERE AND WHEN? No But I wish I did.
8.) HAVE YOU EVER MET THEM? TELL US ABOUT IT! AND IF SO, DO YOU HAVE PICTURES? No I have never met them. :(

9.) FAVORITE SONG OFF OF "ITS ABOUT TIME"? Um....Mandy I think.
10.) FAVORITE SONG OFF OF "JONAS BROTHERS"? Australia for sure.
11.) FAVORITE SONG TO HEAR LIVE? I would have to say Hello Beautiful.
12.) FAVORITE LYRIC? Pop and Lock Battle dance against Hanson.
13.) FAVORITE JONAS BROTHERS TV PERFORMANCE? Arthur Ashe day.
14.) FAVORITE THING ABOUT
     JOE? He is a awesome singer, and is hilarious. Oh and he's hot.
     KEVIN? He's a very good Guitarist.
     NICK? He's a good singer, good drummer/guitarist. Also cute.
15.) FAVORITE JONAS BROTHERS MUSIC VIDEO? S.O.S.

16.) WHICH JONAS BROTHER ARE YOU MOST LIKE? AND HOW? I would have to say that I'm most like Joe. I'm very outgoing, and I don't care what people think of me, so I act crazy a lot of the time.
17.) HYPOTHETICALLY SPEAKING, LETS SAY YOU'RE TRAPPED ON A DESERTED ISLAND. YOU CAN BRING ONE BROTHER AND THREE OBJECTS. WHAT DO YOU CHOOSE? AND WHAT DO YOU DO TO KEEP BUSY? (LETS KEEP THIS PG, KIDS!) I would pick Joe, and I would take...A book...A guitar...and a flashlight. I would probably read, and spend my time making a shelter.
18.) WHAT DO YOU LIKE MOST ABOUT JOBROS FASHION SENSE? HOW ABOUT LEAST? I like it. I think they are very fashionale.
19.) ARE THE BOYS STARING AT YOU FROM VARIOUS ANGLES, VIA POSTERS ON YOUR WALLS? No I'm not allowed to put things on my walls.
20.) POST YOUR FAVORITE JONAS BROTHERS PICTURE!


NOW MORE ABOUT YOU.

21.) 10 FAVORITE BANDS/ARTISTS EVERYONE ELSE SHOULD LISTEN TO? I really only listen to the Jonas Brothers.
22.) 5 FAVORITE MOVIES EVERYONE SHOULD WATCH? Step Up, Any of the Harry Potters, Fever Pitch, She's the Man
23.) 3 FAVORITE BOOKS EVERYONE SHOULD READ? Harry Potter
24.) BEST CONCERT YOU'VE BEEN TO BESIDES THE JONAS BROTHERS? Styx
25.) FIVE RANDOM FACTS ABOUT YOURSELF. I don't have any.
26.) AND LAST BUT NOT LEAST... FACEBOOK/MYSPACE/ANYTHING ELSE? Myspace.

So today is Nick Jonas's brithday. He is turning 15. HAPPY BIRTHDAY NICK J! YOUR OFF THE CHAIN!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

In and Out, 

~Danae~

Hey everybody. 

So today I got to see the Live chat and let me tell you it was hilarious. I love the Jonas Brothers, they are hilarious. Joe played his and Nick's ringtones, and Joe sang to his, and Nick's was the James Bond Theme song, someone said it was the Pink Panther, and Kevin said somehting like "That's not the Pink Panther it's 007." I thought that was pretty funny, but maybe that's just me.

In and Out,
~Danae~
